text: Scheid () is a village and former municipality of the district of Hinterrhein in the canton of Graubünden in Switzerland. On 1 January 2009, the former municipalities of Scheid, Feldis/Veulden, Trans and Tumegl/Tomils merged into the new municipality of Tomils.
